dump: L!This program cannot be run in DOS mode.
Keystroke Panic lets you to change all keystrokes in your computer
(or your victim's) into your own words! Whatever he typed on his
keyboard, the characters will be replaced with your own words.
Keystroke Panic will also automatically run at startup.
1. Type some words to replace all keystrokes in the computer
2. Type the password to stop Keystroke Panic (so it won't run at
3. Give the modified program to your victim
Please remember the password to stop Keystroke Panic, since it will
always run if you don't type the password correctly.
Enter the password to delete the program here
Enter some words to replace all keystrokes here
